- BullMQ
- Redis

### Authentication

- JWT
- Refresh Tokens

### Security

- Helmet
- CORS
- bcrypt
- Express Rate Limit

### Testing

- Vitest
- Supertest

### DevOps

- GitHub Actions
- Node Cluster

