## в–¶ Getting Started

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Zaidshaikh2811/bank_transactions.git
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### Configure Environment

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

### Start Development Server

```bash
npm run dev
```

### Run Tests

```bash
npm test
```

